From Wikipedia

Ola is the third album released by Swedish pop singer Ola.

It was released in Sweden in January 2014, and debuted at #4 in the official Swedish album chart.[1] It is the first release on Sony Music Entertainment. It spawned the hit singles, "I'm in Love" that was a hit for Ola in Italy, his first in that country reaching #4 in the Italian Singles Chart. The album resulted in addition to two minor hits, "Maybe" and "Jackie Kennedy", the latter charting again in Italy.
